      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software used under FDA-recognized quality management system with version control and audit trail.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2 deployed under 21 CFR Part 11-compliant QMS. Version control logs and installation qualification records reviewed and found satisfactory."
