      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual norms and energy convergence criteria met within solver tolerances for all load steps.",
      "rationale": "Force and displacement residuals converged to 1e-6 relative tolerance for all 11 model instances. No non-convergence events recorded across the full load history."
    },
    {
