      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and load application by analyst not involved in original model construction.",
      "rationale": "Secondary analyst reviewed all boundary condition definitions, contact pair assignments, and material property inputs against the simulation plan. No discrepancies identified."
