      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric parameters sourced from certified coupon tests and CMM measurements with documented uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength derived from ASTM E8 tensile coupons (n=5 per lot). Geometric dimensions from CMM reports with ±0.01 mm tolerance. Uncertainty propagation via Latin Hypercube sampling (1000 draws) confirmed QoI sensitivity within acceptable bounds."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
