      "rationale": "Mean absolute percentage error on construct stiffness: 4.2% across N=11 pairs. All FEA predictions fall within experimental 95% confidence interval. U-pooling validation metric = 0.87, exceeding 0.80 threshold."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
