      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs selected for validation directly correspond to quantities used in the regulatory decision context.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield load are the primary QoIs validated here and are the same quantities cited in the 510(k) substantial equivalence argument. Direct traceability established in the simulation plan."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
